---
// About section with personality
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 px-6">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
		<!-- Section header -->
		<div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-16">
			<span class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">01</span>
			<h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
				About me
			</h2>
			<span class="flex-1 h-px bg-ink/10 dark:bg-ink-dark/10"></span>
		</div>

		<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
			<!-- Photo / Visual -->
			<div class="lg:col-span-5">
				<div class="relative">
					<!-- Placeholder for photo with creative frame -->
					<div
						class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative group"
					>
						<!-- Gradient placeholder -->
						<div
							class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/20 via-clay/10 to-transparent"
						>
						</div>

						<!-- Abstract pattern overlay -->
						<svg
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-10"
							viewBox="0 0 100 100"
							preserveAspectRatio="none"
						>
							<defs>
								<pattern
									id="grid"
									width="10"
									height="10"
									patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
								>
									<path
										d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10"
										fill="none"
										stroke="currentColor"
										stroke-width="0.5"></path>
								</pattern>
							</defs>
							<rect
								width="100"
								height="100"
								fill="url(#grid)"
								class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark"></rect>
						</svg>

						<!-- Photo placeholder text -->
						<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
							<span class="font-mono text-sm text-stone dark:text-stone-dark"
								>[ your photo here ]</span
							>
						</div>

						<!-- Decorative corner -->
						<div
							class="absolute top-4 left-4 w-8 h-8 border-l-2 border-t-2 border-accent"
						>
						</div>
						<div
							class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 w-8 h-8 border-r-2 border-b-2 border-accent"
						>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Floating badge -->
					<div
						class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-paper dark:bg-paper-dark px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg border border-ink/5 dark:border-ink-dark/5"
					>
						<span class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Available for work</span
						>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Bio content -->
			<div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-6">
				<p class="text-lg text-stone dark:text-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
					I'm a developer who believes the best code is the code that
					<span class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark font-medium">disappears</span
					>â€”leaving only a seamless experience. Based somewhere on the internet,
					I spend my days turning designs into reality and my nights debugging
					why that one thing
					<em class="font-display italic text-accent">almost</em> works.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-stone dark:text-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
					My journey started with curiosity about how websites work, which led
					me down the rabbit hole of frontend development. Now I build
					full-stack applications, but my heart still skips a beat for a
					perfectly crafted component or a buttery-smooth animation.
				</p>

				<p class="text-lg text-stone dark:text-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
					When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring new frameworks (yes,
					another one), contributing to open source, or convincing myself that
					this side project will definitely be finished.
				</p>

				<!-- Quick facts -->
				<div class="pt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
							Currently
						</h3>
						<p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
							Building cool stuff & learning
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
							Previously
						</h3>
						<p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
							Various projects & experiments
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
							Education
						</h3>
						<p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
							Self-taught + Internet University
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent">
							Interests
						</h3>
						<p class="text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
							Web perf, Design systems, DX
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
